import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { Link, useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import '../styles/Session.css' const Session = ({ API_URL }) => { const params = useParams() const [session, setSession] = useState({}) const [exercisesSession, setExercisesSession] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { const getSession = async () => { await fetch(`${API_URL}/sessions/${params.id}`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(data => setSession(data)) } const getExercisesSession = async () => { await fetch(`${API_URL}/exercisesSessions/${params.id}`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(data => setExercisesSession(data)) } getSession() getExercisesSession() }, [API_URL, params.id]) return (

{session.name}

{exercisesSession.map(ex => ( ))}
Ejercicio Series Repeticiones RIR Descanso Observaciones
{ex.name} {ex.series} {`${ex.minReps}-${ex.maxReps}`} {ex.RIR} {`${ex.rest}"`} {ex.observations}
Volver
) } export default Session
